description:
MOPH Car Rental Services :- 

We offer car rental services to individuals and families for either short or long term rentals. 
Cheap and reasonable rates for daily and weekly rentals. 
Freebies for any person who rents for 2 weeks onwards! 

*Rates : 

- Enquire within directly for more competitive prices. 

*For half day rental, only near USJ & Subang Jaya areas are allowed.
*Rate for 2 weeks & 1 month is negotiable.
- Free delivery for renting 3 days and above only at certain locations. (Call/Message for more info) 

Documents required : 

1. IC photocopy (front & back) or Passport (Front & Permit details) 
2. Driving License copy (front & back) 
3. Student card (if any) - 5% off on total rental. (Please include a photocopy as well) 
4. 1 Utility bill copy (water/electricity/TM/astro/staff ID) 
5. *Guarantor IC & License copy (if tenant is below the age of 21 yrs old/renting a place or is a foreigner) 
6. Security deposit (refundable) - RM 100 for daily and/or up to 3 days, RM200 for 4 and/or up to a week and RM 300 for monthly rentals. 

*If renter is staying at a rented place, kindly include landlord's details for security purposes. 
*Must be Malaysian citizen. 

Car Model & Feature set : 

Perodua Axia (G) 1.0 (Auto) 
Silver colour. 
5 seater vehicle. 
Well maintained and clean interior. 
LED Daylight saving lights in the front for added safety. 
Music experience enhanced with booster installed. 
With JPJ approved security and solar tint for your added convenience and safety. 
Semi leather seats instead of fabric for added comfort. 

Terms & Co. 
 
Require few days notice for monthly rentals. 
First come first serve basis. 
Upfront payment is required before getting the keys. 
WA preferred, 7 days a week*. 
*Only messages will be entertained after 10pm on weekdays.
